    "He bequeathed his collection of drawings to the city of Groningen, while the Amsterdam Rijksprentenkabinet acquired 65 Rembrandt drawings.": [],
    "He donated his Italian medals to the municipal Museum of The Hague.": [],
    "Smaller donations also went to the museums of Haarlem and Leiden.": [],
    "But old animosities remained even after his death.": [],
